WEBVTT

00:00:00.976 --> 00:00:04.120
So, this happy pic of me
was taken in 1999.

00:00:04.144 --> 00:00:06.234
I was a senior in college,

00:00:06.258 --> 00:00:08.190
and it was right after a dance practice.

00:00:08.214 --> 00:00:09.732
I was really, really happy.

00:00:10.328 --> 00:00:14.214
And I remember exactly where I was
about a week and a half later.

00:00:14.238 --> 00:00:17.457
I was sitting in the back
of my used minivan

00:00:17.481 --> 00:00:19.244
in a campus parking lot,

00:00:19.268 --> 00:00:20.419
when I decided

00:00:20.443 --> 00:00:22.222
I was going to commit suicide.

00:00:23.976 --> 00:00:28.013
I went from deciding
to full-blown planning very quickly.

00:00:28.568 --> 00:00:31.563
And I came this close
to the edge of the precipice.